---
title: Chipotle-Beef Flatbreads with Caramelized Onions and Feta
description: Smoky, sweet and spicy is the name of the game with this super-simple beef flatbread recipe. Chipotle sauce provides the perfect base, while caramelized onions bring a subtle sweetness to offset the heat from the jalapeños.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pains-plats-au-boeuf-et-au-chipotle-841d8aa2.jpg
